venue.name: Black Canyon (แบล็คแคนยอน)

tip.text: Foods are good and delicious. Try on their signature dish - Spicy salmon, you have an option for French fries or mashed potatoes for the side. Baked escargot cheese taste good but small in size.
A place for special occasion such as birthday party & celebration. Music is loud which you have to raise your voice while talking to the person next to you 😅😅
Foods taste good with unlimited refilled of side dishes. However, abit expansive.
Price increase but the food portion drop... So disappointed 😣
My all time favourite 👍🏻 Good service & good foods. Set lunch available from Monday - Saturday, quite worth it. Also, try mud pie, yummy dessert that you can't missed it 👍🏻
Must try the signature French toast, it's soft & fluffy. So yummy but slightly expensive.
Service is good, a must try their signature Xiao long bao. Recommend sour & spicy soup and sesame dumpling in soya milk.
Ordered D24 Durian sticky rice, expected to be durian meat but the actual dessert served is totally different from the picture shown on menu. It actually durian ice-cream. Felt being cheated 😓

formattedAddress: The Gardens Mall (Lot LG-228A, LG Floor)

venue.name: Hui Lau Shan Healthy Dessert 許留山

tip.text: Portion for kimchi combo is quite small, kimchi soup taste good but just filled 1/3 of the cup. Place for catch up with friends but not recommend for lunch / dinner place. Unless you are small eater.
Service is quite good. Recommended this place to meat lover! However, papaya shake is too sweet and taste like mixture of milk & syrup, no papaya taste.
First try set lunch - seafood ramen. 1 prawn + 2 clams.. Side dish can't refill. Overall so so, not as per expected.

contact.facebookName: Woo Ga Chon - Korean BBQ & Restaurant

tip.text: Taste of ramen not bad, good to try. However, the lemon drinks seems to be diluted..
Sharing portion, it will be a great place for chocolate lovers! Limited seats. Recommend salon chocolate crepe, options to choose either strawberry or banana filling

tip.text: Limited choice of foods & lack of food storage (I think) as before 7.30pm left only pork belly. Wanton is small and not whole shrimp as stated in menu. Price overrated with small portions of foods.
